<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(معقل)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> قال: قال عمر: لا <span class="c2">(تتبعني)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> امرأة <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
